and it's nodulated by a different genus, Mesorhizobium, species loti.


196
0:12:8,4 --> 0:12:9,9
And the system that I study,


197
0:12:9,9 --> 0:12:13,433
which is the genus Medicago, which includes alfalfa,


198
0:12:13,433 --> 0:12:17,733
and which is nodulated by Sinorhizobium meliloti.


199
0:12:17,733 --> 0:12:19,6
This is the species you'll hear about,


